snippet.title: Homeworld Mobile - PAX West Teaser
snippet.description:
Learn more ➡ https://www.homeworldmobile.com

Homeworld Mobile (working title) extends Homeworld to a new galaxy and a new platform. Guarantee early access to Homeworld Mobile by backing Homeworld 3 at https://www.fig.co/homeworld3. 
Sign up for news at https://www.homeworldmobile.com and expect to hear more from Fleet Command soon.
